msgid "Has access to `ANNOTATION_STORE`, `QUALIFIERS`, `INTERCEPTOR_BINDINGS`, `STEREOTYPES`, `BEANS` (class-based beans only), `OBSERVERS` (class-based observers only), `INJECTION_POINTS`"
